document_data.mainbody:
Corinna was a squirrel that lived in or around the Emerald Grove during the late 15 century DR.
In the , Corinna and another squirrel named Spar encountered the tiefling woman Alfira, singing and playing her lute at a secluded spot in the druids grove. The nutty pair deemed her performance so terrifyingly awful that the two squirrel friends could barely stand to be in her presence.
